casebody.data:
Anthony Baron YOUNG, Personal Representative of the Estate of Ken Young, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
WALTON OIL, INC., Defendant-Appellant. SC: 157533
COA: 333794 Supreme Court of Michigan. June 14, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the February 6, 2018 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
